l:dependency.name: JSHint Report Plug-in
l:dependency.l:description: This plug-in generates the trend report for JSHint reports in Checkstyle format. JSHint is an open source static code analysis program.

The Apache projects are characterized by a collaborative, consensus based development process, an open and pragmatic software license, and a desire to create high quality software that leads the way in its field. l:dependency.name: Xerces2 Java Parser
l:dependency.l:description: Xerces2 is the next generation of high performance, fully compliant XML parsers in the Apache Xerces family. This new version of Xerces introduces the Xerces Native Interface (XNI), a complete framework for building parser components and configurations that is extremely modular and easy to program.
